    tests. Dist rebuilt (tsc clean); ENV_REFERENCE + lib/README updated. Documented in
    the 009 packet. launcher-lease is pre-existing-red in this environment (fails on
    HEAD with these changes stashed). Activation: next daemon load + a full
    code_graph_scan to drop existing markdown nodes.

